OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783973917
OL,3,CFormer Foreign Office chief sacked by
OL,4,CStarmer launches legal challenge
OL,6,FThe former Foreign Office chief, who
OL,7,Fwas sacked by Sir Keir Starmer over
OL,8,FLord Peter Mandelson's security
OL,9,Fvetting, has submitted a legal
OL,10,Fchallenge over his dismissal.
OL,12,FSir Olly Robbins has requested a
OL,13,Fjudicial review after he was removed
OL,14,Fas the top civil servant at the
OL,15,FForeign Office in April 2026.
OL,17,FRobbins is being represented by the
OL,18,FFDA Union, who have filed the case
OL,19,Fclaiming Robbins was given
OL,20,F"irrational" reasons for being fired.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
