FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783973917
OL,3,CFormer Foreign Office chief sacked by
OL,4,CStarmer launches legal challenge
OL,6,FThe submission made the case that
OL,7,FStarmer had no statutory authority to
OL,8,Fdismiss him as the head of the
OL,9,Fdiplomatic service and that there was
OL,10,F"no fair procedure" and "no process at
OL,11,Fall" in his dismissal.
OL,13,FRobbins said he brought the challenge
OL,14,F"reluctantly".
OL,16,F"It would have been unnecessary if the
OL,17,Fprime minister had simply apologised
OL,18,Ffor his mistake and made amends for
OL,19,Fthe distress and cost it has caused me
OL,20,Fand my family," he said in a statement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783973917
OL,3,CFormer Foreign Office chief sacked by
OL,4,CStarmer launches legal challenge
OL,6,FThe statement continued: "Instead, I
OL,7,Fnow have to ask the courts to
OL,8,Fdetermine that the Prime Minister's
OL,9,Fdecisions were unlawful, unreasonable
OL,10,Fand to quash them."
