PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783973917
OL,3,CFormer Foreign Office chief sacked by
OL,4,CStarmer launches legal challenge
OL,6,FStarmer sacked Robbins in April after
OL,7,Fit emerged the department was
OL,8,Fresponsible for overruling a decision
OL,9,Fby UK Security Vetting not to grant
OL,10,FPeter Mandelson clearance before he
OL,11,Fwas appointed Washington ambassador.
OL,13,FThe former top civil servant has
OL,14,Frepeatedly said that he was prevented
OL,15,Ffrom giving ministers any details
OL,16,Fabout security vetting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
