PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1783973917
OL,3,CFormer Foreign Office chief sacked by
OL,4,CStarmer launches legal challenge
OL,6,FThe FDA union said Robbins' dismissal
OL,7,Fwas "based on a grievous
OL,8,Fmisunderstanding" of how the vetting
OL,9,Fprocess works and also "a rash
OL,10,Fresponse to a media story".
OL,12,FIn April 2026, Starmer defended the
OL,13,Fsacking and claimed that the evidence
OL,14,Fpresented that Robbins hid information
OL,15,F"puts to bed all the allegations
OL,16,Flevelled at me".
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
